msgstr "Œuvre supprimée"

#: includes/Publishing/ReviewConfirm.php:129
msgid "Link expired or already used"
msgstr "Lien expiré ou déjà utilisé"

#: includes/Publishing/ReviewConfirm.php:133
msgid "The artwork has been published to the gallery."
msgstr "L’œuvre a été publiée dans la galerie."

#: includes/Publishing/ReviewConfirm.php:134
msgid "The submission has been discarded."
msgstr "L’envoi a été supprimé."

#: includes/Publishing/ReviewConfirm.php:135
msgid "Your artwork has been removed from the gallery."
msgstr "Votre œuvre a été retirée de la galerie."

#: includes/Publishing/ReviewConfirm.php:136
msgid ""
"This link may have already been used or may have expired. Please log in to "
